title: After 6-year wait, 6-year-old undergoes surgery at AIIMS Delhi

description: Chris Gayle and Ian Bishop congratulated the Indian team for winning the ICC T20 World Cup title, particularly Virat Kohli, who announced his retirement from T20Is. Virat Kohli, the second-highest T20I run-scorer with 4,188 runs, scored 76 off 59 balls in the final against South Africa, helping India reach 176/7.
title: 'Best way to go': Legends praise Kohli as he retires from T20Is

description: India clinched the T20 World Cup title in a fierce battle against South Africa at Kensington Oval, with Virat Kohli's retirement announcement adding to the intensity of the match, showcasing the team's resilience and determination in securing the victory.
title: Why Anand Mahindra ‘called’ ChatGPT after India’s World Cup win

description: After India's historic triumph against South Africa for the T20 World Cup title, a relieved and happy Rohit was addressing a press conference in Barbados with the trophy on his side. And a journalist asked the Indian captain if it was getting difficult for him to keep faith on goodness and whether good things happen to good people, whether it's Rohit himself or the team or Rahul Dravid.
title: Watch - 'Yehi toh khel hai...': Rohit Sharma's hilarious reply

description: Inspector Sanjay Gupta led the team using technical surveillance while the father maintained continuous phone contact with the kidnapper during the high-speed chase and rescue operation in Samaypur Badli.
title: Siblings kidnapped with car as parents go to buy sweets
2nd batch of 4,029 pilgrims leave for Amarnath

description: Amit Shah asserts BJP's readiness to contest Haryana polls independently, highlighting PM Modi's achievements. Shah appreciates key contributors and criticizes Congress leaders for corruption, emphasizing BJP's worker-centric approach.
title: BJP to fight Haryana polls alone: Amit Shah

description: Mrinmay Talukdar, a young photographer, tragically ended his life while live-streaming on Facebook. The incident took place in Bhaskar Nagar area, and depression may have played a role. The live-stream started around 3 pm, leaving behind a mystery regarding the reasons for the actions.
title: Photographer ends life during Facebook live in Assam

description: Soon after India's title victory, a video went viral that shows both Virat Kohli and Rohit Sharma celebrating with the Indian flag by wrapping the 'Tiranga' on their shoulders with Rohit also holding the T20 World Cup trophy. Virat Kohli and Rohit Sharma both announced their retirements from the shortest format of the game in international cricket. Having played in all nine editions of the shortest format, Rohit leaves a lasting legacy.
title: Watch: Virat Kohli and Rohit Sharma celebrate with India flag

description: A student from Jhalawar Govt Medical College was involved in a paper leak scam using dummy candidates to exploit reservation quotas in tribal regions, affecting recruitment exam fairness.
title: NEET-UG row: College student appeared as dummy candidate
